lead_paragraph: Iowa agriculture officials say bird flu could claim an additional four million of Iowa’s egg-laying chickens on two more farms in a county already hit by the disease.

headline.print_headline: Iowa: Bird Flu May Claim 4 Million More Chickens
headline.main: Iowa: Bird Flu May Claim 4 Million More Chickens
